About Efficacity

   Efficacity is a research and development centre dedicated to urban
   energy transition. Launched in 2014 with state support via the
   investments for the future programme (PIA), it unites on a single site
   the skills of over 100 researchers from backgrounds in industry,
   engineering and public research.
   Learn more

